It is no longer news that one of Nigeria foremost hospitality giant, the Wells Carlton Hotels & Apartment has blaze the trail again by redefining out door delivery through digital medium. The 5 star international luxury hotel renowned for its excellent world class services in the hospitality industry  has delved into food outlet services aimed at providing meals of international standard to customers. This innovative concept according to Wells Carlton Sales Manager, Opiughie Aloye Jerry said the take out is the “answer to an increasing demand for grill based fast food. Opiughie explained that since the launch of Wells grill take out in the nation’s capital Abuja,  it has afforded  both the young and old a new meal experience not known before adding that it is a conscious effort in trying bring restaurant to your homes. “The Wells grill take out strive to be a premier local fast food brand in the local market place. We want our customers to have the total experience when ordering from our digital platforms and websites as they will learn about this fascinating new, ‘pop culture’ created around fast food delivery with technology” “We will in the future expand our service to sell merchandise from pre-package sauces and T-shirt to potato cutters, all with our official brand attached to them in a bid to further build on this pop culture. Our main focus will be serving high quality at a great value in a timely and hygienic process.” 